# Kubernetes background

- An application orchestrator
- It orchestrates containerized cloud-native microservices apps

# Orchestrator
	System that deploys and manage applications

	Kubernetes can:
		1. Deploy app
		2. Scale it up and down
		3. Self heal
		4. Perform zero-downtime updates/rollbacks
		5. And more
		You only need to set it up

# Containerised app
	App that runs in a container
	Kubernetes can also orchestrate VMs and serveless functions


